  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "MulRan focuses on range sensor-based place recognition and provides 6D baseline trajectories of a vehicle for ground truth place recognition.",
    "This dataset is expected to promote the development of range-LiDAR based place recognition technology.",
    "Yin et al. (2021) introduced Radar-to-LiDAR, a heterogeneous measurement-based framework for long-term place recognition.",
    "This method retrieves query radar scans from an existing LiDAR map.",
    "Initially, the radar and LiDAR points are encoded using Scan Context (Kim and Kim 2018) and then a shared U-Net transforms the handcrafted features to learned representations."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
